                    Criadero de Gatos Persas en Sevilla con Envíos a Toda España
                </h1>
                <div class="w-32 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#FF6B6B] to-pink-400 mx-auto mb-8"></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 mb-20">
                <div class="group relative bg-white p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-[0_10px_40px_-15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-3 overflow-hidden border border-gray-50">
                    <div class="absolute -top-10 -right-10 w-32 h-32 bg-pink-50 rounded-full transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-[3] -z-10"></div>
                    
