                        🏠
                    </div>
                    
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4 text-[#2E2E2E] group-hover:text-[#FF6B6B] transition-colors">
                        Hogar Familiar
                    </h3>
                    
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base">
                        En <strong>Ágatha Gatos Persas</strong> nos especializamos en la cría responsable de <strong>gatos persas</strong>. Cada uno de nuestros gatitos crece en un hogar lleno de amor y cuidado, garantizando salud, belleza y un temperamento equilibrado.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="group relative bg-white p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-[0_10px_40px_-15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-3 overflow-hidden border border-gray-50">
                    <div class="absolute -top-10 -right-10 w-32 h-32 bg-blue-50 rounded-full transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-[3] -z-10"></div>
                    
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-[#F0F7FF] rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-3xl mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500">
                        🚚
                    </div>
                    
